action.text: Mr. Smith (WA) asked unanimous consent to consider as introduced.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: This concurrent resolution makes a correction in the enrollment of H.R. 7776 (James M. Inhofe National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2023) to amend the official title of the bill.
